org.transitime.utils.csv

Class CsvBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.utils.csv.CsvBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AvlCsvRecord, GtfsAgency, GtfsCalendar, GtfsCalendarDate, GtfsFareAttribute, GtfsFareRule, GtfsFeedInfo, GtfsFrequency, GtfsRoute, GtfsShape, GtfsStop, GtfsStopTime, GtfsTransfer, GtfsTrip

    public class CsvBase
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for CSV struct classes. The main CSV struct classes must inherit from this class. Keeps track of line numbers. Also handles errors when necessary data is missing in CSV file.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
